OL,3,CMan accused of Leicestershire arson
OL,4,Cattacks declared unfit to stand trial
OL,6,FA 50-year-old man accused of a spate
OL,7,Fof arson attacks in Leicestershire has
OL,8,Fbeen declared unfit to stand trial due
OL,9,Fto a psychotic illness, a judge has
OL,10,Fruled.
OL,12,FThe fires, which injured three people
OL,13,Fin Ashby-de-la-Zouch, took place on
OL,14,FHolywell Avenue, Prestop Drive and
OL,15,FClifton Drive on Friday 21 November
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
