OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776971469
OL,3,CMan accused of Leicestershire arson
OL,4,Cattacks declared unfit to stand trial
OL,6,FKarl Poxon, 50, was arrested and
OL,7,Fcharged with multiple counts of arson
OL,8,Fand has been in custody since the
OL,9,Ffires. He has not entered pleas to the
OL,10,Foffences of intent to endanger life,
OL,11,Fas well as one count of dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FA trial date had been set for the week
OL,15,Fbeginning Monday 11 May. But after two
OL,16,Fpsychiatrists examined Poxon, they
OL,17,Fdeemed he was unfit to plead.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776971469
OL,3,CMan accused of Leicestershire arson
OL,4,Cattacks declared unfit to stand trial
OL,6,FAt Leicester Crown Court, prosecutor
OL,7,FGary Short said: "The defendant has
OL,8,Fbeen seen by two approved
OL,9,Fpsychiatrists and they both agree he
OL,10,Fis unfit.J"The latest report showed
OL,11,Fdeterioration."
OL,13,FMr Short said the experts also agreed
OL,14,FPoxon needed hospital treatment but
OL,15,Fwas stuck in prison waiting for a
OL,16,Fhospital bed to become available. He
OL,17,Fadded that the original trial date
OL,18,Fwould not be able to determine
OL,19,Fcriminal guilt or establish if Poxon
OL,20,Fhad started the fires.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
