FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776971469
OL,3,CMan accused of Leicestershire arson
OL,4,Cattacks declared unfit to stand trial
OL,6,FSteven Newcome, representing Poxon,
OL,7,Fsaid that the trial of facts should go
OL,8,Fahead with the original date.
OL,10,FJudge Rebecca Herbert said that having
OL,11,Fread the psychiatric reports that Mr
OL,12,FPoxon is "not fit to stand trial".
OL,14,FShe added "I express the hope he is
OL,15,Ftransferred (to hospital)".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
